<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>사진의아름다움 on GGG Pick 아트소품</title><link>https://art.gggpick.com/tags/%EC%82%AC%EC%A7%84%EC%9D%98%EC%95%84%EB%A6%84%EB%8B%A4%EC%9B%80/</link><description>Recent content in 사진의아름다움 on GGG Pick 아트소품</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>ko-kr</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 08:02:59 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://art.gggpick.com/tags/%EC%82%AC%EC%A7%84%EC%9D%98%EC%95%84%EB%A6%84%EB%8B%A4%EC%9B%80/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>사진 프레임의 선택- 아크릴 프레임 vs 나무 프레임</title><link>https://art.gggpick.com/20260607-0802-%EC%82%AC%EC%A7%84-%ED%94%84%EB%A0%88%EC%9E%84%EC%9D%98-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D-%EC%95%84%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%B4-%ED%94%84%EB%A0%88%EC%9E%84-vs-%EB%82%98%EB%AC%B4-%ED%94%84%EB%A0%88%EC%9E%84/</link><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 08:02:59 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://art.gggpick.com/20260607-0802-%EC%82%AC%EC%A7%84-%ED%94%84%EB%A0%88%EC%9E%84%EC%9D%98-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D-%EC%95%84%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%B4-%ED%94%84%EB%A0%88%EC%9E%84-vs-%EB%82%98%EB%AC%B4-%ED%94%84%EB%A0%88%EC%9E%84/</guid><description>&lt;div class="mx-5 px-5 mt-3 pt-3 mb-3 mb-sm-4 d-none d-md-block">
